99-0651 (La. 4/23/99)

Sherry CLIFTON v. DITTO’S APPAREL. Sherry Clifton v. Ditto’s Apparel. No. 99-C-0651. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Ditto’s Apparel; Executive Risk Consultants Inc; — Defendant(s); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Office of Workers’ Compensation Dist. 2 Number 96-03871, 94-08199; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98-1180, CA98-1181

Denied.

MARCUS, J. not on panel. VICTORY and TRAYLOR, JJ. would grant the writ.
